                  allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
              </div>
              <h3>Python Sentiment Analysis Project with NLTK and Transformers. Classify Amazon Reviews!!</h3>
              <p>
                In this video you will go through a Natural Language Processing Python Project creating a Sentiment Analysis classifier with NLTK's 
                VADER and Huggingface Roberta Transformers. The project is to classify the seniment of amazon customer reviews
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="tutorial-box">
              <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe
                  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Bdc55j80l8"
                  title="Illustrated Guide to Transformers Neural Network: A step by step explanation"
